        <abstract>
            <p>Asks whether his observations on absorptive powers of glandular hairs of plants are new facts.</p> 
<p>Asks for a <hi rend="italic">Drosophyllum</hi>.</p>  
<p>Comments on Francis Galton’s article in <hi rend="italic">Fraser’s Magazine</hi>,</p>  
<p>Greg’s <hi rend="italic">Enigmas</hi>,</p>  
<p>and Alphonse de Candolle’s <hi rend="italic">Histoire des sciences</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
